Created 1.4.1948 out of the parish of Polesworth. See also Table 
    2, notes (j) and (l).

On 25.3.1885 the part in Leicestershire  became part of the parish of Orton on the Hill, so that thereafter Merevale 
    was entirely in Warwickshire. See also Table 2, notes (a), (b), (c) and (l).
